---
import DocsLayout from '../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
import CodeBlock from '../../components/CodeBlock.astro';
import ExampleSection from '../../components/ExampleSection.astro';
---

<DocsLayout title="Shell Layout" description="Complete application layout structure.">
  <article class="space-y-12">
    <header class="border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 pb-8">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Shell Layout</h1>
        <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full border bg-success/10 text-success border-success/30">stable</span>
      </div>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 max-w-2xl">
        The shell layout provides the structural foundation for the entire application, including header, sidebars, main content area, and footer.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Structure Overview</h2>
      
      <div class="p-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-surface/50">
        <div class="border-2 border-dashed border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
          <!-- Header -->
          <div class="h-12 bg-theme-primary/20 border-b-2 border-dashed border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-700 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-xs font-mono text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Header</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex">
            <!-- Left Sidebar -->
            <div class="w-16 md:w-24 h-48 bg-theme-primary/10 border-r-2 border-dashed border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-700 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-xs font-mono text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 [writing-mode:vertical-lr]">Left Sidebar</span>
            </div>
            <!-- Main Content -->
            <div class="flex-1 h-48 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-xs font-mono text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Main Content</span>
            </div>
            <!-- Right Sidebar -->
            <div class="w-16 md:w-24 h-48 bg-theme-primary/10 border-l-2 border-dashed border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-700 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-xs font-mono text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 [writing-mode:vertical-lr]">Right Sidebar</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Footer -->
          <div class="h-10 bg-theme-primary/20 border-t-2 border-dashed border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-700 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-xs font-mono text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Footer</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <CodeBlock 
        language="html"
        filename="shell-layout.html"
        code={`<div class="flex flex-col h-screen">
  <!-- Header -->
  <header class="h-14 bg-white dark:bg-surface border-b border-slate-200 dark:border-border">
    <!-- Header content -->
  </header>
  
  <!-- Content wrapper -->
  <div class="flex flex-1 overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Left Sidebar -->
    <aside class="w-64 border-r border-slate-200 dark:border-border bg-white dark:bg-surface">
      <!-- Sidebar content -->
    </aside>
    
    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main class="flex-1 overflow-y-auto bg-white dark:bg-obsidian">
      <!-- Page content -->
    </main>
    
    <!-- Right Sidebar (optional) -->
    <aside class="w-64 border-l border-slate-200 dark:border-border bg-white dark:bg-surface">
      <!-- Panel content -->
    </aside>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Footer (optional) -->
  <footer class="h-12 bg-white dark:bg-surface border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-border">
    <!-- Footer content -->
  </footer>
</div>`}
      />
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Usage Guidelines</h2>
      <div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
        <ul class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 space-y-2">
          <li>The shell layout uses <code>h-screen</code> and <code>overflow-hidden</code> to contain all content within the viewport</li>
          <li>The main content area uses <code>overflow-y-auto</code> for independent scrolling</li>
          <li>Sidebars are optional and can be toggled on mobile devices</li>
          <li>Use <code>custom-scroll</code> class for styled scrollbars</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
</DocsLayout>




